title: 'Back to the Future' fans transform town into Hill Valley
text:
> Entertainment 'Back to the Future' fans transform town into Hill Valley "Back To The Future" fans line up in front of downtown Fillmore's movie theater to watch a screening of the documentary film "Back In Time" during Fillmore's celebration of the movie franchise on Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015, in Fillmore, Calif.
